  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras/e40eb87e8a24c71149eefb391ed20d7a.poster.avif?t=1741247048\" width=608 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras/e40eb87e8a24c71149eefb391ed20d7a.webm?t=1741247048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras/e40eb87e8a24c71149eefb391ed20d7a.mp4?t=1741247048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Hunt the Pale Gods is roguelike tactical deck-builder, hunt horrific monsters and use their powers against them.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add powerful cards to your deck, loot ancient curios that break the rules of the game and discover wild synergies. Nightmarish bosses wait to test you and your deck, with unique card rewards that stack the odds in your favour. You will need it.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RUN DEFINING CARDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras/a744945b6fb603f343931ff658cce287.avif?t=1741247048\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras_big/a744945b6fb603f343931ff658cce287.avif?t=1741247048 width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you defeat a powerful foe, you will be offered extremely rare divine cards. They unlock wild synergies and combos, making every run unique and changing the way you play the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >APOSTLES TO THE PALE GODS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras/ad4677036fe6d32ceac2a38853c1502e.poster.avif?t=1741247048\" width=608 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras/ad4677036fe6d32ceac2a38853c1502e.webm?t=1741247048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras/ad4677036fe6d32ceac2a38853c1502e.mp4?t=1741247048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You will face five different aspects of the <strong>Pale Gods</strong>. Each aspect has unique foes, mechanics, and card rewards. Shape your deck, discover game breaking combinations, and <strong>awaken your true potential</strong>. No run is the same!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PRIMORDIAL: Savagery and blood magic. Call upon the primal strength surging within.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PROGENY: Time and space. Manipulate reality and the flow of time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ABYSSAL: Wrath from the deep. Command sea and stone to crush anyone in your way.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UMBRAL: The dark beyond. Lurk in the shadows and become the terror in the void.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >EYE: The cult of the Ashen Absolution. Ancient secrets and cleansing flames.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EVERY STEP COUNTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras/5985e540c65dd392fa43d319fcadac02.poster.avif?t=1741247048\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras/5985e540c65dd392fa43d319fcadac02.webm?t=1741247048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras/5985e540c65dd392fa43d319fcadac02.mp4?t=1741247048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Battles flow, standing still means defeat. <strong>Movement</strong> and <strong>positioning</strong> are critical. Dodge enemy attacks, rush in on the offense, steal the powerful altars and utilize the terrain features to your favor. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OVERWHELM AND STAGGER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras/498e2b549fcddf86aebba77fe66f31d0.poster.avif?t=1741247048\" width=608 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras/498e2b549fcddf86aebba77fe66f31d0.webm?t=1741247048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras/498e2b549fcddf86aebba77fe66f31d0.mp4?t=1741247048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Press the attack, break your foes and force them to <strong>STAGGER</strong>. Use this window to obliterate them or catch your breath. Be careful, you are just as easily staggered. Plan and control the battle! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VEILED  PATH</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras/9c29a9be2b22ae4c58ffe473525f368f.poster.avif?t=1741247048\" width=608 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras/9c29a9be2b22ae4c58ffe473525f368f.webm?t=1741247048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997060/extras/9c29a9be2b22ae4c58ffe473525f368f.mp4?t=1741247048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The path ahead is uncertain. Each individual path choice matters now, it defines the next battle and the card rewards you will be offered. The future is unknown, do not waste time. Choose wisely, choose boldly! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURE LIST</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >250+ Unique cards, to unleash upon your enemies. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >120+ Curios, with game breaking effects. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >11 Characters, with their own mechanics. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40+ Events, with unique choices that shape your run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >13 Horrifying bosses, that stand in your way.</p></li></ul>",
